This is a massive step up from the 5minutes map. It now includes water, indoor areas and more detailed environments. Please download it and tell me what to improve. I've added in some features that I'm not if sure they will be popular or not, but the only way to improve a map is to try new things.

THANK YOU FOR YOUR SUGGESTIONS...
rockerdudeman
